attempts.sparql_query: PREFIX nas: <http://www.semanticdesktop.org/ontologies/2007/04/18/nas#> SELECT ?depAirport1 ?depAirport2 WHERE { ?flight1 a nas:Flight ; nas:departureAirport ?depAirport1 . ?flight2 a nas:Flight ; nas:departureAirport ?depAirport2 . FILTER ( ?depAirport1 = <http://www.semanticdesktop.org/ontologies/2007/04/18/nas#AAL1170> && ?depAirport2 = <http://www.semanticdesktop.org/ontologies/2007/04/18/nas#ASQ3831> ) }
attempts.query_explanation: This query checks if the departure airports of flights AAL1170 and ASQ3831 are located in the same country by filtering for the specific flight URIs.
